 --><h3>End of life care</h3><!-- end field b03bf966-f818-47df-8f80-16c38c8ae032 -->","summary":null,"htmlStringContent":"<!-- begin item 74d43286-b2d7-4db0-86b1-873e363c2d4b --><!-- begin field 33b04e62-6b4e-4c96-9754-ff7c55b8b773 --><ul><li>It can often be difficult to be certain that a person is dying, but it is essential to recognize the signs of dying in order to appropriately care for people at the end of life. For more information see the CKS topic <a class=\"topic-reference external-reference\" href=\"/topics/palliative-care-general-issues/\">Palliative care - general issues</a>. </li><li>An individualised care plan including the areas of symptom control and anticipatory prescribing should be created. For more information see the CKS topic <a class=\"topic-reference external-reference\" href=\"/topics/palliative-care-general-issues/\">Palliative care - general issues</a>. </li></ul><!-- end field 33b04e62-6b4e-4c96-9754-ff7c55b8b773 --><!-- end item 74d43286-b2d7-4db0-86b1-873e363c2d4b -->","subChapters":[{"id":"7eb7a34d-61af-5338-b8f2-f95e8e949ef7","slug":"basis-for-recommendation-50a","fullItemName":"Basis for recommendation","depth":4,"htmlHeader":"<!-- begin field f72ea103-cc36-40a6-81fb-adc03d8e5f66 --><h4>Basis for recommendation</h4><!-- end field f72ea103-cc36-40a6-81fb-adc03d8e5f66 -->","summary":null,"htmlStringContent":"<!-- begin item 50abc143-df3b-4d5f-b9b3-551521f2bddc --><!-- begin field 9286d247-da13-48c4-9637-39431fdbb5f4 --><p>These recommendations are largely based on the National Institute for Health and Care Excellence (NICE) guideline <em>Care of dying adults in the last days of life</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/palliative-care-constipation/references/\">NICE, 2015a</a>] Care of dying adults in the last days of life. The basis for the NICE recommendations has been briefly summarized in this section. For detailed information on the evidence NICE used to make these recommendations, see the full <a href=\"https://www.nice.org.uk/guidance/ng31/chapter/Recommendations\" data-hyperlink-id=\"f681e51c-aeb6-4592-9df6-a98d00324e69\">NICE guideline.</a></p><!-- end field 9286d247-da13-48c4-9637-39431fdbb5f4 --><!-- end item 50abc143-df3b-4d5f-b9b3-551521f2bddc -->","subChapters":[]}]}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3666801979"]}